name: UrbanGlitch_Metro
description:
A new animated .gif from my UrbanGlitch series, where I want to show how the city handles its own shapes. In this .gif the subway passes in an infinite loop while the passenger / spectator waits to get in, but never succeeds.

It's made with 12 .jpeg in low exposure.

2048x1347px
.gif
Infinite loop.
